{"tid":2236884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lunch哥同好鍾意報lunch哥嘅媒體同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-10-09T22:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T10:53:29.000Z","uid":13586,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"12760585fdae073835463f5d9ece2e511809d929","tid":2236884,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T22:17:26.000Z","msg":"Lunch哥，你有呢份堅持，成日出席甚至自發和你lunch，keep住個抗爭嘅温度，我好欣賞<br />\n<br />\n但你唔好再膠化成場抗爭，冇料到冇撚用就縮返後面咪喺度充大頭鬼！<br />\n<br />\n之前有巴打share咗呢啲罪狀，你自己好好返省下呢排你嘅所作所為，係有幾令手足厭惡！<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">李國永重大罪狀：\n1. 周梓樂祭壇前玩汽水撚狗，對死者極不尊重。\n\n2. 性騷擾女手足，將自己條J send俾人睇。\n\n3. 膠化抗爭，用佢所謂嘅行為藝術同埋活動令到運動成為一場笑話。\n\n4. 自稱全香港最成功勇武，開咗個全港最大勇武公海，喺裏面自以為指揮幫人安排職位同埋更表。\n\n5. 大搞個人崇拜，成立左一個星級團隊。\n\n6. 與狗握手，連gphone都忍唔住話你。\n\n7. telegram/Instagram一言堂獨裁，巔峰時期一日300個ban。對抗爭毫無幫助。\n\n8. 喺工程巴囚車面前搞事，令到其家人冇得送車。\n\n9. 唔聽意見，所有批評/比建議佢嘅人都會俾佢屈做藍屍以及分化撚。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n而家可以加多個<br />\n10. 朗屏同黑警合作拉手足<br />\n<br />\n呢排我推緊德國聯署都睇唔過眼，如果澄清返我跟車太貼嘅，你自己都好好鳩縮返入老母個閪度，唔好膠化運動做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於好鍾意報lunch哥嘅傳媒，好似蘋果，毛記：<br />\n係呀我點名呀，你哋有份助長佢條on9仔嘅氣焰，我知道呢個都有機會可以做你嘅新聞，但唔好再特別focus 呢條撚樣度，佢係零新聞價值ok？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於Avant Vision Square，香港人連儂牆，好&middot;傳媒：<br />\n日日咁多手足上庭又唔報，幾多黃店因為國安法而淆底又唔報，喺度幫條垃圾搞個人祟拜，同而家渣哥龍門屌嚟屌去有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n出面有政府林鄭習種中共狗咁多嘢唔屌喺度玩內鬥，就算之後澄清返朗屏呢單唔關你地事，你哋都zip高枕頭諗吓條撚屌仲值唔值得為你哋科水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後麻煩admin：<br />\n希望呢個post只係出現今日10月10號，10月11號零時零分之後勞煩admin你幫手del post，費事啲lunch gor 啲小fans話返我「你而家咪又係一樣玩緊內鬥～」<br />\n但我同你哋講，<strong>佢而家仲衰過過街老鼠呀</strong>，藍絲們想要呢啲咁嘅豬隊友我自己個人絕對歡迎佢過主！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後都唔該10月10號：<br />\n黃店任：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzZJ9Ru.jpg&amp;h=5c0ad823&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月20號前：<br />\n德國聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0932e4e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrances.huiwingting%2Fvideos%2F776349853204218&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=910f9290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGfmbAf.jpg&amp;h=9dfa0e7b&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"04150f5b3da94eca0b4cbf2c3e608470f6e91459","tid":2236884,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T22:20:54.000Z","msg":"蘋果不嬲鬼鬼地嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過非建制就大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢d報導好多時為吸引人睇就得  冇政治考慮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經日日幫手維穩做恐懼撚  夠標題性就得"},{"pid":"919a805f80b2489e12d2642264305647b6822a5f","tid":2236884,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T22:21:34.000Z","msg":"黃店任：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzZJ9Ru.jpg&amp;h=5c0ad823&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月20號前：<br />\n德國聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0932e4e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrances.huiwingting%2Fvideos%2F776349853204218&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=910f9290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn